nd Warstorm","quest_id":140000004},{"text":"General, you flatter me.","quest_name":"Grand Warstorm","quest_id":140000004},{"text":"I've heard people comparing the Norfall Barrens to a massive graveyard. Whenever it rains, cries and moans can be heard, as if many ghosts are weeping...","quest_name":"Grand Warstorm","quest_id":140000004},{"text":"Master once told me life and death should follow a natural course. The heavens and the earth form a vast chamber, where spirits freely depart and return.","quest_name":"Grand Warstorm","quest_id":140000004},{"text":"Countless brave souls have been trapped here by the evil powers of Ovathrax. I want to help set them free.","quest_name":"Grand Warstorm","quest_id":140000004}]}